Description:
    Configuration generator for node module loopback-ssl (https://www.npmjs.com/package/loopback-ssl)

Options:
    option1: HTTP - Default loopback configuration
    option2: HTTPS - Loading certificates from files
    option3: HTTPS -  Loading certificates from files & Mutual SSL authentication

Example:
    yo loopback-ssl

    This will update (server directory):
        server.js: Updated server.js including loopback-ssl configuration
        config.json: Certificate configuration for looopback-ssl
        package.json: Development packages installed by npm.
